name: EASY-LOD Demo Moved
body:
You reached the original location of **EASY Metadata as Linked Open Data Demo** repository, now available under DANS-labs account.

Please check https://github.com/dans-labs/easy-lod/ for latest developments
and http://dans-labs.github.io/easy-lod/ for an up-to-date description of
the project.
